      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nPrakash, there is a check in mkfs_lustre.c:\n\n\tif ((IS_MDT(ldd) || IS_OST(ldd)) && mop.mo_ldd.ldd_fsname[0] == '\\0') {\n\t\tfatal();\n\t\tfprintf(stderr, \"Must specify --fsname for MDT/OST device\\n\");\n\t\tret = EINVAL;",
